OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FThe sexual offences trial of Sir
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson has heard a church
OL,8,Fpastor state an alleged victim told
OL,9,Fhim she could not report abuse because
OL,10,Fit would "destroy" the former DUP
OL,11,Fleader's "political reputation".
OL,13,FThe trial at Newry Crown Court also
OL,14,Fheard from the founders of a Christian
OL,15,Fcentre who stated that Donaldson had
OL,16,Fsaid "sorry" to the alleged victim in
OL,17,Fthe 1990s, but added that no
OL,18,Fallegations had been mentioned during
OL,19,Fthe meeting.
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@RO]sD@JOUsD@_O]xD@FOUxD@LO]
