OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780859470
OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FEx-MP Donaldson, 63, has pleaded not
OL,7,Fguilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,9,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,10,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,11,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,12,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008 involving
OL,13,Ftwo alleged victims.
OL,15,FComplainant A and B have both
OL,16,Fpreviously given evidence at the
OL,17,Fsexual offences trial.
OL,19,FLady Eleanor Donaldson denies several
OL,20,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,21,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
