OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,8,FOn Friday, the jury of seven men and
OL,9,Ffive women heard evidence from Laura
OL,10,FClaire Selfridge, who is the daughter
OL,11,Fof David and Linda Hoy, who founded
OL,12,Fthe Christian Family Centre in Armoy,
OL,13,FCo Antrim.
OL,15,FThe court has previously heard
OL,16,Fevidence that Complainant B had stayed
OL,17,Fat the centre when she was a teenager
OL,18,Fafter developing a problem with drugs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
