OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FMs Selfridge told the court she had a
OL,7,Fconversation with Complainant B in her
OL,8,Fbedroom in Armoy.
OL,10,FShe told the court: "She literally
OL,11,Fjust said she had been abused."
OL,13,FWhen asked about the atmosphere, Ms
OL,14,FSelfridge said: "Very shocking, almost
OL,15,Flike a bomb went off, that is what it
OL,16,Ffelt like for me."
OL,18,FThe witness added: "She was very
OL,19,Ftroubled, I remember feeling my heart
OL,20,Fwas very raw for her."
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@_O]vD@QOUxD@RO]zD@TOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
