OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FThe witness said they had never spoken
OL,7,Fagain about the alleged abuse.
OL,9,FWhen asked if she had spoken to anyone
OL,10,Felse about the alleged abuse, she
OL,11,Fsaid: "Never, not to this day."
OL,13,FJeffrey Donaldson's barrister Kieran
OL,14,FVaughan KC asked the witness if
OL,15,FComplainant B had used the word
OL,16,F"sexual" in relation to the alleged
OL,17,Fabuse.
OL,19,FShe replied "No".
OL,26,@sD@GOUsD@_O]xD@AOUxD@HO]{D@MOU{D@PO]
