OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FHe said she had wanted to talk about
OL,7,Fsomething but told him: "I don't want
OL,8,Fanybody to know this."
OL,10,FHe said: "I listened to her and she
OL,11,Fmade very, very serious allegations."
OL,13,FHe added: "She looked like somebody
OL,14,Fthat had come through the wars."
OL,16,FMr Matthews said he then introduced
OL,17,Fher to David and Linda Hoy, because
OL,18,Fthey could provide counselling.
OL,20,FThe pastor said she told him she had
OL,21,Fbeen abused when "very young".
