OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FHe said he had asked her why she did
OL,7,Fnot "come out with this and get help".
OL,9,FHe added: "She said she can't because
OL,10,Fit would destroy their political
OL,11,Freputation, I don't want that."
OL,13,FMr Matthews said he could not remember
OL,14,Fif B had named her alleged abuser but
OL,15,Fsaid it "became obvious" who it was.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@eO]qD@KOUsD@_O]wD@IOUwD@XO]
