OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FHe said: "I think that she had said he
OL,7,Fwas rising through the ranks of the
OL,8,FOfficial Unionist Party, he was from
OL,9,FKilkeel, he was assistant to a
OL,10,Fprevious MP and was as such would be
OL,11,Fin line to become an MP."
OL,13,FAsked by a police officer who he
OL,14,Fbelieved that to be, Mr Matthews said:
OL,15,F"There was only one person, that was
OL,16,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson."
OL,18,FMr Hoy then gave evidence at the trial.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@YO]wD@AOUxD@WO]
