OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FHe told the jury he had received a
OL,7,Fphone call from Mr Matthews in the
OL,8,F1990s stating there "had been an
OL,9,Fallegation".
OL,11,FHe added: "He said it was against
OL,12,FJeffrey Donaldson."
OL,14,FThe witness added: "I knew it was
OL,15,Fserious but I didn't really know what
OL,16,Fthe nature of the allegations was."
OL,18,FMr Hoy said Complainant B was looking
OL,19,Fto meet Donaldson and "wanted a safe
OL,20,Fplace to do that".
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@KO]sD@KOUtD@SO]vD@TOUxD@cO]{D@
