OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FThe witness said he then arranged a
OL,7,Fmeeting between himself and Donaldson
OL,8,Fat a hotel.
OL,10,FMr Hoy said he told Donaldson "there
OL,11,Fhad been an allegation...and she
OL,12,Fwanted to meet him face to face".
OL,14,FAsked about Donaldson's response, he
OL,15,Fsaid: "It was positive, in fact it
OL,16,F(the meeting) was arranged for the
OL,17,Fnext day."
OL,26,@rD@_OUtD@`O]wD@GOUyD@JO]
