OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780859470
OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FMr Hoy said he asked B if she wanted
OL,7,Fto "take this any further and she said
OL,8,Fno".
OL,10,FHe said there had been no discussion
OL,11,Fat the meeting of what the allegations
OL,12,Fwere. He added that it had been a
OL,13,Fbrief meeting.
OL,15,FHe also told the jury that he and his
OL,16,Fwife had subsequently seen Jeffrey and
OL,17,FEleanor Donaldson to provide
OL,18,Fcounselling about "marital problems".
OL,26,@oD@DOUpD@CO]zD@SOUzD@dO]
