OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FBarrister for Jeffrey Donaldson Kieran
OL,7,FVaughan KC asked if allegations had
OL,8,Fbeen made at the meeting in the Hoys'
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FMr Hoy said: "None."
OL,13,FMr Vaughan suggested that Complainant
OL,14,FB had said at the meeting that she had
OL,15,F"not been comfortable at times in the
OL,16,Frelationship" with Donaldson.
OL,18,FHe further suggested Donaldson had
OL,19,Fsaid "if that was the case he
OL,20,Fapologised".
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@TO]wD@AOUxD@MO]{D@FOU|D@KO]
