OL,3,CDonaldson abuse not reported as it
OL,4,Cwould 'destroy reputation', trial told
OL,6,FMr Hoy responded: "It could have been
OL,7,Fsaid but I don't recall it."
OL,9,FLinda Hoy then gave evidence about the
OL,10,Fsame meeting.
OL,12,FShe said: "Mr Donaldson said I know
OL,13,Fwhat this is about, I am truly sorry,
OL,14,Fplease forgive me."
OL,16,FShe said Complainant B had responded
OL,17,F"yes".
OL,19,FThe trial will resume on Monday.
